{
    "$schema": "https://getcomposer.org/schema.json",
    "name": "laravel/react-starter-kit",
    "type": "project",
    "description": "The skeleton application for the Laravel framework.",
    "keywords": [
        "laravel",
        "framework"
    ],
    "license": "MIT",
    "require": {
        "php": "^8.2",
        "inertiajs/inertia-laravel": "^2.0",
        "laravel/framework": "^12.0",
        "laravel/tinker": "^2.10.1",
        "resend/resend-php": "^0.18.0",
        "spatie/laravel-permission": "^6.19",
        "tightenco/ziggy": "^2.4"
    },
    "require-dev": {
        "fakerphp/faker": "^1.23",
        "laravel/pail": "^1.2.2",
        "laravel/pint": "^1.18",
        "laravel/sail": "^1.41",
        "mockery/mockery": "^1.6",
        "nunomaduro/collision": "^8.6",
        "pestphp/pest": "^3.8",
        "pestphp/pest-plugin-laravel": "^3.2"
    },
    "autoload": {
        "psr-4": {
            "App\\": "app/",
            "Database\\Factories\\": "database/factories/",
            "Database\\Seeders\\": "database/seeders/"
        }
    },
    "autoload-dev": {
        "psr-4": {
            "Tests\\": "tests/"
        }
    },
    "scripts": {
        "post-autoload-dump": [
            "Illuminate\\Foundation\\ComposerScripts::postAutoloadDump",
            "@php artisan package:discover --ansi"
        ],
        "post-update-cmd": [
            "@php artisan vendor:publish --tag=laravel-assets --ansi --force"
        ],
        "post-root-package-install": [
            "@php -r \"file_exists('.env') || copy('.env.example', '.env');\""
        ],
        "post-create-project-cmd": [
            "@php artisan key:generate --ansi",
            "@php -r \"file_exists('database/database.sqlite') || touch('database/database.sqlite');\"",
            "@php artisan migrate --graceful --ansi"
        ],
        "dev": [
            "Composer\\Config::disableProcessTimeout",
            "npx concurrently -c \"#93c5fd,#c4b5fd,#fb7185,#fdba74\" \"php artisan serve\" \"php artisan queue:listen --tries=1\" \"php artisan pail --timeout=0\" \"npm run dev\" --names=server,queue,logs,vite"
        ],
        "dev:ssr": [
            "npm run build:ssr",
            "Composer\\Config::disableProcessTimeout",
            "npx concurrently -c \"#93c5fd,#c4b5fd,#fb7185,#fdba74\" \"php artisan serve\" \"php artisan queue:listen --tries=1\" \"php artisan pail --timeout=0\" \"php artisan inertia:start-ssr\" --names=server,queue,logs,ssr"
        ],
        "test": [
            "@php artisan config:clear --ansi",
            "@php artisan test"
        ]
    },
    "extra": {
        "laravel": {
            "dont-discover": []
        }
    },
    "config": {
        "optimize-autoloader": true,
        "preferred-install": "dist",
        "sort-packages": true,
        "allow-plugins": {
            "pestphp/pest-plugin": true,
            "php-http/discovery": true
        }
    },
    "minimum-stability": "stable",
    "prefer-stable": true
}

message.content:
In this view, http://business-process.test/business-processes/1/cores/3?tab=raci, we have a Add Activity button, we need to 
  add a new button to "Import HTML", this import button should open a new select file and parse the HTML content, to:\
  \
  1. Extract the Activities Category (class="section-header") 
  2. Extract the Activities and create the RACI entry\
  3. Add the relationshipt between the Category and activity\
  4. This import will override all the RACI activities in the core process\
  5. We may want to store the HTML as the "Visual Diagram" Content, then if the RACI activities change this "Visual Diagram" should be updated based on the changes\
\

  The HTML sample is: \
\
<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

    <meta charset="UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

    <title>Acquira Accelerator: Sale to Delivery Process</title>

    <style>

        body {

            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;

            margin: 0;

            padding: 20px;

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #3498db 100%);

            min-height: 100vh;

        }



        .container {

            max-width: 1600px;

            margin: 0 auto;

            background: white;

            border-radius: 15px;

            padding: 30px;

            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);

        }



        h1 {

            text-align: center;

            color: #2c3e50;

            margin-bottom: 30px;

            font-size: 28px;

            font-weight: 700;

        }



        .process-section {

            margin-bottom: 40px;

        }



        .section-header {

            font-size: 20px;

            font-weight: bold;

            margin-bottom: 20px;

            padding: 15px;

            border-radius: 8px;

            color: white;

            text-align: left;

        }



        .blueprint .section-header {

            position: relative;

            cursor: pointer;

            transition: all 0.3s ease;

        }



        .blueprint .section-header:hover {

            transform: translateY(-3px);

        }



        .blueprint .section-header::after {

            content: "PROCESS BLUEPRINT";

            position: absolute;

            top: 50%;

            right: 20px;

            transform: translateY(-50%);

            font-size: 11px;

            font-weight: bold;

            opacity: 0.9;

            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);

            padding: 6px 12px;

            border-radius: 12px;

            transition: all 0.3s ease;

            white-space: nowrap;

            letter-spacing: 0.5px;

            text-transform: uppercase;

        }



        .blueprint .section-header:hover::after {

            opacity: 1;

            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);

        }



        .blueprint.contract-payment .section-header {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c, #c0392b);

            border: 2px solid #c0392b;

            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.3);

        }



        .blueprint.contract-payment .section-header:hover {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ec7063, #e74c3c);

            border-color: #e74c3c;

            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.4);

        }



        .blueprint.customer-onboarding .section-header {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #27ae60, #229954);

            border: 2px solid #229954;

            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.3);

        }



        .blueprint.customer-onboarding .section-header:hover {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #52c882, #27ae60);

            border-color: #27ae60;

            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(39, 174, 96, 0.4);

        }



        .blueprint.program-setup .section-header {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f39c12, #e67e22);

            border: 2px solid #e67e22;

            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.3);

        }



        .blueprint.program-setup .section-header:hover {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5b041, #f39c12);

            border-color: #f39c12;

            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.4);

        }



        .blueprint.transition-handoff .section-header {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9b59b6, #8e44ad);

            border: 2px solid #8e44ad;

            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.3);

        }



        .blueprint.transition-handoff .section-header:hover {

            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #bb8fce, #9b59b6);

            border-color: #9b59b6;

            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.4);

        }



        .process-flow {

            display: flex;

            flex-wrap: wrap;

            gap: 20px;

            justify-content: center;

            align-items: flex-start;

        }



        .step-box {

            background: white;

            border-radius: 12px;

            padding: 20px;

            width: 280px;

            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);

            border: 3px solid #3498db;

            position: relative;

            transition: all 0.3s ease;

        }



        .step-box:hover {

            transform: translateY(-5px);

            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);

        }



        .step-box::before {

            content: "QUICK GUIDE";

            position: absolute;

            top: -10px;

            left: 15px;

            background: #3498db;

            color: white;

            padding: 4px 8px;

            border-radius: 4px;

            font-size: 10px;

            font-weight: bold;

        }



        .step-title {

            font-size: 16px;

            font-weight: bold;

            color: #2c3e50;

            margin-bottom: 10px;

            line-height: 1.3;

        }



        .step-desc {

            font-size: 14px;

            color: #5a6c7d;

            margin-bottom: 15px;

            line-height: 1.4;

        }



        .raci {

            font-size: 12px;

            color: #7f8c8d;

            background: #f8f9fa;

            padding: 8px;

            border-radius: 6px;

            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;

            line-height: 1.3;

        }



        .arrow {

            position: absolute;

            right: -25px;

            top: 50%;

            transform: translateY(-50%);

            width: 0;

            height: 0;

            border-top: 12px solid transparent;

            border-bottom: 12px solid transparent;

            border-left: 20px solid #95a5a6;

            z-index: 5;

        }



        .insights-section {

            margin-top: 30px;

            padding: 20px;

            background: #f8f9fa;

            border-radius: 8px;

            border-left: 4px solid #3498db;

        }



        .insights-section h3 {

            margin-top: 0;

            color: #2c3e50;

        }



        .insights-section ul {

            color: #5a6c7d;

            line-height: 1.6;

        }



        @media (max-width: 768px) {

            .step-box {

                width: 100%;

            }

            .arrow {

                display: none;

            }

        }

    </style>

</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">

        <h1>Acquira Accelerator: Sale to Delivery Process</h1>



        <!-- Blueprint Phase 1: Contract & Payment -->

        <div class="process-section contract-payment blueprint">

            <div class="section-header">Contract & Payment Processing</div>

            <div class="process-flow">

                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Contract Generation</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Generate Accelerator enrollment agreement with customer details and program terms</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Sales Operations | A: Josh Harris | C: Acquisition Advisor</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Payment Processing</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Process $12,500 payment via Stripe, confirm receipt, update customer status in Salesforce</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Sales Operations | A: Josh Harris | C: N/A</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Internal Sales Handoff</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Transfer customer information from sales team to delivery team with deal summary</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Acquisition Advisor | A: Josh Harris | C: Andi</div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>



        <!-- Blueprint Phase 2: Customer Onboarding -->

        <div class="process-section customer-onboarding blueprint">

            <div class="section-header">Customer Onboarding & Qualification</div>

            <div class="process-flow">

                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Welcome & Orientation Call</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Conduct welcome call to set expectations, explain program structure, and confirm readiness</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Andi | C: Acquisition Advisor</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Financial Qualification Verification</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Verify $50K+ available funds, 670+ credit score, and SBA eligibility requirements</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Nathan | C: Dana</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Investment Thesis Development</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Guide customer through developing their investment criteria and target business profile</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Nathan | C: Dana</div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>



        <!-- Blueprint Phase 3: Program Setup -->

        <div class="process-section program-setup blueprint">

            <div class="section-header">Program Access & Materials Setup</div>

            <div class="process-flow">

                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Thinkific Course Enrollment</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Enroll customer in Accelerator course platform and send login credentials</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Andi | C: N/A</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Slack Community Access</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Add customer to private Acquira Slack community for peer interaction and support</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Andi | C: N/A</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Tools & Templates Delivery</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Provide access to financial models, SOPs, playbooks, and M&A templates via course platform</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Andi | C: Penelope</div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>



        <!-- Blueprint Phase 4: Transition to Delivery -->

        <div class="process-section transition-handoff blueprint">

            <div class="section-header">Transition to Service Delivery</div>

            <div class="process-flow">

                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Investment Committee Scheduling</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Schedule customer for weekly group coaching calls and deal review sessions</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Andi | C: Dana</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Coach Assignment</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Assign primary coach (Dana/Rich) based on customer profile and availability</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Andi | A: Andi | C: Dana</div>

                    <div class="arrow"></div>

                </div>



                <div class="step-box">

                    <div class="step-title">Service Delivery Handoff</div>

                    <div class="step-desc">Complete handoff to delivery team with customer ready to begin Accelerator training</div>

                    <div class="raci">R: Nathan | A: Andi | C: Assigned Coach</div>

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>



        <div class="insights-section">

            <h3>Process Flow Insights:</h3>

            <ul>

                <li><strong>Nathan's Central Role:</strong> Handles majority of onboarding steps from welcome call through platform setup</li>

                <li><strong>Andi's Oversight:</strong> Provides accountability across most delivery preparation processes</li>

                <li><strong>Josh Harris Accountability:</strong> Maintains control over contract and payment processes</li>

                <li><strong>Coach Integration:</strong> Dana and Rich consulted early to prepare for smooth handoff</li>

                <li><strong>Clean Process Flow:</strong> Clear progression from sales completion to delivery readiness</li>

                <li><strong>Quality Gates:</strong> Financial verification and investment thesis development ensure qualified customers</li>

            </ul>

        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>\
